{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC06_NIO_610.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x22,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Well, I think this is all for the time being... I need to put away all the equipment I used."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "Hmm? Is something wrong?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "Sis, you clean up after yourself?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "That's right, after I'm done working. Is that weird?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Weird or funny or...I was just surprised."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Sis, you're able to keep things tidy and organized now."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "Before, I had to clean everything up or it would turn into a disaster."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Yeah. I didn't intend to make a mess, but before I knew it, the room was always such a mess..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "And the workshop was like a garbage dump when you first disappeared."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "Sis, you don't see the world around you when you start working..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "Sometimes Ernie would stop by, and he'd help me clean up..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x138,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Whaaat! You made Ernie clean up for you!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13a,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "Even if it is Ernie, you can't make him do thaaat!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "Hahaha...I couldn't tell him then, but I did feel bad. He said..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "\"You haven't been able to concentrate on your work at all since Nio disappeared, so just leave this to me.\""
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13c,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "But that has nothing to do with me disappearing..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13d,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "You were never able to clean up after yourself."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yeah...so I felt really bad and..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "I thought to myself, \"Nio would laugh at me.\" So then, I did my best to tidy up and get organized."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x13e,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "I see. I can't believe you're able to clean up after yourself now..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x15e,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "But, now that I'm back, you can make a mess like before."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x160,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "I'll do all the household chores!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Hmm, but now I'm used to being tidy and organized..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15b,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "I think it'll be hard to go back..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x76,
            "expr_id": 0x3,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "Boo! I want to help you out."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x78,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "I have one less thing to do..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "It's fine, you're still a child,<CR>Nio, so you can just help me out<CR>from time to time."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Okay, then I'll go gather some medicinal herbs!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "Right now? Umm...don't stay out too late, okay? I mean it's right after what just happened and all..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x195,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "Yup, okay. I'm going to the usual place, so I think it'll be fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Be careful. Don't trip and fall from running."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x6,
            "name_id": 0x6,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "I'll be fiiine. Okay, I'm going!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "(I'm a little worried,<CR>but...I think it'll bother<CR>Nio if I'm overprotective...)"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "(As the older sister, I should just watch over her... Ugh, but I'm still worried...)"
        }
    ]
}